metadata.name: LaFerrari #1
metadata.description:
Only 1 LaFerrari in Mexican territory and I had the opportunity to do a shooting with it. 

This 1/1 piece comes with a full size print signed by me shipped anywhere in the world and also the opportunity to join me in a photoshoot in Mexico City.

I'm very grateful for the support of my work. That is what keeps me motivated to create more art for all of you.
